[normal]              
[normal]Mrs Moon:[bold] Sorry?
[normal]              
[normal]Professor Wessely:[bold] They certainly do it but they don’t know if it works, because they didn’t do a trial. Our trial is actually funded by the Americans, not because they love us but because it dawned on them that it was a very silly thing to introduce an incredibly expensive policy that might well do more harm than good without evidence. 
[normal]              
[normal]Mrs Moon:[bold] And not do any analysis?
[normal]              
[normal]Professor Wessely:[bold] And not do the trial, yes. The 
[normal]US
[normal] are paying for this trial in the 
[normal]UK
[normal] because they should have done it in the 
[normal]US
